{"tid":991011,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【表格都炒！？！】代印4000蚊表格　港男疑網售圖利","createTime":"2019-01-22T05:19:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-22T05:34:40.000Z","uid":225464,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"eea9b5ff9f4c3e5e2e5bd01193a3c1c50dbf8909","tid":991011,"uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T05:19:48.000Z","msg":"<strong>代印4000蚊表格　港男疑網售圖利　網民轟呃錢</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190122/bkn-20190122125318759-0122_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190122%2Fbkn-20190122125318759-0122_00822_001.html&d=hvi0Gj61P2aDcx%2Bz4nMIp8mB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=7f37f591\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190122/bkn-20190122125318759-0122_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190122/photo/bkn-20190122125318759-0122_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190122131048\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190122%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190122125318759-0122_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190122131048&h=fe864c0d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n表格都可以賣？"},{"pid":"21471dc6212a2370fdb34d0d2acfdfa0ef89f6a8","tid":991011,"uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T05:20:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190122/photo/bkn-20190122125318759-0122_00822_001_02p.jpg?20190122131048\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190122%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190122125318759-0122_00822_001_02p.jpg%3F20190122131048&h=a698e525&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n該男子在多個群組發貼宣傳。（互聯網）"},{"pid":"ef5aa23f02113b612529079b9e96da75b4198d9e","tid":991011,"uid":225464,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T05:20:22.000Z","msg":"申領4000港元的關愛共享計劃的首批申請表昨日（21日）於多區派罄。有人疑趁機化為賺錢途徑，在網上表示只要繳付10元郵費，就會「送出」一份申請表格，惹來網民批評。<br />\n<br />\n有男子昨日在Facebook群組「Hk MaMa &amp; Bb 全新二手用品買賣」發貼，指會「免費送出4000元申請表格一份，連申請須知共10張紙」，但收取者需繳付10元「郵費」。<br />\n<br />\n有網民質疑他趁機賺錢，但男子反駁道︰「免費幫你哋印，紙錢、印費、郵費唔使錢呀？抵你們4000蚊咁難攞&hellip;包埋填表，寄埋，幫你交埋表好不好」、「份申請須知6張紙，還有郵費5.2蚊呢」。<br />\n<br />\n不少網民留言斥責：「一個二個以免費作招徠呃錢」、「畀10蚊請人幫手填表都嫌貴啦」、「幾張紙，寄去外國都唔使10蚊」。有人則轟政府安排失當︰「派4000蚊派到咁真係唔知講乜好」。"},{"pid":"bb841aa68eadb4f5b47894150d37e4a846ea8481","tid":991011,"uid":106233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T05:28:01.000Z","msg":"商機"},{"pid":"b6c6ceedf23017015b91d2220afb3998b0dacb8d","tid":991011,"uid":139967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T05:32:05.000Z","msg":"香港有咩唔可以賣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c11c5f0e519da723bd72f74068c04de8c0e5c58","tid":991011,"uid":2300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T05:34:40.000Z","msg":"上門裝icq <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}